        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Northern Border Reopening Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits applying to any Canadian national any limitations or suspensions on entry into the United States that are based on a COVID-19 travel restriction.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
